/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a car on the road, giving a driver's eye view of the scene. The street is lined with lush green trees, providing a stark contrast to the clear blue sky above. Cars of various colors are scattered along the road, hinting at the city's vibrant life. Buildings of different heights and designs flank the street, showcasing the architectural diversity of the city. Power lines crisscross above, a common sight in urban landscapes. The image is bathed in the light of a sunny day, casting soft shadows and highlighting the textures of the buildings and trees.
